{"tid":1909213,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"差唔多畢業 好似搵到想做嘅野","createTime":"2020-03-03T20:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T12:12:07.000Z","uid":151721,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3364c5c7447c51fbf40a93883551e69a04275698","tid":1909213,"uid":151721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T20:56:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n畢咗業想做去外國orchestra做administration 或者management 嘅嘢，呢啲位係咪通常有music degree 先做到？定係讀cultural management 或者art administration 嘅master都得？<br />\n<br />\n自己學咗音樂好多年 但係知自己一定係想唔到台嘅人 所以想用另一個方法做對個樂界畀小小貢獻 我知係個好on9嘅諗法 希望各位畀小小建議或者直接屌醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bdb551c5d46f5e7f4f70be9efe2cb0cd5532f84","tid":1909213,"uid":207470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T20:58:36.000Z","msg":"add oil"},{"pid":"12a7eafbdfa1ed5c7ebb725ab006c1c728a4a648","tid":1909213,"uid":315529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T20:59:42.000Z","msg":"trytry佢啦"},{"pid":"46499c0fd688b7a8f8bc72d9fe27881f6b70b931","tid":1909213,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T20:59:56.000Z","msg":"加油啊 我都係非三大社科出身"},{"pid":"69503736be4acb20b75b56d9a48fea314f0c35fc","tid":1909213,"uid":16713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T20:59:57.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n我都想知自己想做咩<br />\n利申畢咗業無做嘢成年"},{"pid":"2c2af753d3af3bdc60b74336f2dc163938d30dbb","tid":1909213,"uid":315529,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T21:00:18.000Z","msg":"屋企冇負擔就周圍試吓"},{"pid":"aad132f5f3e44cfd10978f03d1a57a9a505f13c2","tid":1909213,"uid":198245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69503736be4acb20b75b56d9a48fea314f0c35fc","tid":1909213,"uid":16713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T20:59:57.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n我都想知自己想做咩<br />\n利申畢咗業無做嘢成年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-